text: Nancy Allen (born on June 24, 1950) is an American movie and television actress. She was born in Yonkers, New York. Her movies include Carrie (1976), RoboCop (1987), RoboCop 2 (1990) and RoboCop 3 (1993). ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from New York (state) Category:People from Yonkers, New York
